                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>At the beginning of each of its turns in combat, a cursed king must attempt a @Check[type:flat|dc:2]. If it succeeds, the DC increases by 1. If it fails, it immediately goes berserk, becoming mindless for the rest of its turn, immune to all mental effects, and attacking the nearest creature it can reach. While it's berserk, each of its unarmed attacks gain the deadly d8 trait. At the end of a turn it failed this flat check or whenever the combat encounter ends, the DC resets to 2.</p>"
